sentences.sentence: Anita Loos was in many respects untypical of the screenwriting trade.
sentences.translation: 从很多方面来看，安妮塔•卢斯都不能算是编剧界的代表性人物。

sentences.sentence: Schools in this area are quite untypical of schools in the rest of the country.
sentences.translation: 这个地区的学校根本不能代表全国其他地区的学校。

sentences.sentence: Yet in some ways they were untypical.
sentences.translation: 从某些方面看，他们也不是那么的特殊。
